  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY AS A CAMERAHEAD IN SKIBIDI TOILET GAME</strong>:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558110/extras/9a09634f54cf6120085dc5cf6b806318.poster.avif?t=1729178075\" width=600 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558110/extras/9a09634f54cf6120085dc5cf6b806318.webm?t=1729178075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558110/extras/9a09634f54cf6120085dc5cf6b806318.mp4?t=1729178075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Protect the earth and flush those toilets! Try to get all the materials necessary to build a radio-titan and deal a final blow to the enemy faction.  Make sure to have your teammates protect you when you assault the enemy base as a tv titan, you don't want to lose it! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY AS A SKIBIDI TOILET</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558110/extras/e31a59182e05d724987c73559e1a2a6b.poster.avif?t=1729178075\" width=600 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558110/extras/e31a59182e05d724987c73559e1a2a6b.webm?t=1729178075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558110/extras/e31a59182e05d724987c73559e1a2a6b.mp4?t=1729178075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Embrace the chaos as a member of the Toilets, don't let your enemies build a titan by building your own toiletto-giant first! Crush your enemy with numbers and dance on their graves. Don't let tactics or teamwork slow you down, just rush them and dominate the game. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>JUST HAVE FUN!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558110/extras/3a85c741466481ff5f1ddc341cef84e4.poster.avif?t=1729178075\" width=600 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558110/extras/3a85c741466481ff5f1ddc341cef84e4.webm?t=1729178075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558110/extras/3a85c741466481ff5f1ddc341cef84e4.mp4?t=1729178075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>I don't care if you want to save the earth or conquer it. Just have fun, turn your enemies into trash, and dump them into the garbage bin. It's a game, JUST HAVE SOME SKIBIDI GAME FUN TIME!</p>",
